San Domingo Revolution</em> (1938; repr., New York: Vintage, 1989),
85‚Äì86.¬†<a href="#fnref:1" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;</a></p>
    </li>
    <li id="fn:2" role="doc-endnote">
      <p>C. L. R. James, <em>World Revolution, 1917‚Äì1936: The Rise and Fall of
