role of Leninist internationalism in the rise of anticolonialism
after 1917, a phenomenon he terms ‚ÄúTricontinentalism‚Äù and of which
James is among the most eminent representatives.¬†<a href="#fnref:3" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#x21a9;&#xfe0e;</a></p>
