    <li id="fn:4" role="doc-endnote">
      <p>This is a question that I raised in a previous essay, without
adequately formulating an answer; see Nick Nesbitt, ‚ÄúFragments of a
Universal History,‚Äù in Charles Forsdick and Christian H√∏gsbjorg,
eds., <em>The Black Jacobins Reader</em> (Durham, NC: Duke University
